OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,FThe water sector is in need of "root-
OL,7,Fand-branch reform", a committee of MPs
OL,8,Fhas said as it called for "much more
OL,9,Fregulated management" of bonuses for
OL,10,Fsenior bosses.
OL,12,FThe cross-party Environment, Food and
OL,13,FRural Affairs committee has said that
OL,14,Fthe industry is "failing", but that
OL,15,Fwater companies are "deaf to the
OL,16,Fcrisis" that it is facing.
