OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,FIn their report, Priorities For Water
OL,7,FSector Reform, released on Monday, the
OL,8,FMPs argue that the UK Government
OL,9,F"should feel able to use its temporary
OL,10,Fnationalisation powers" when needed.
OL,12,FThey also said the system should
OL,13,F"ensure that more money gained from
OL,14,Finvestors and through customer bills
OL,15,Fis directed towards investment in
OL,16,Fwater infrastructure and service
OL,17,Fdelivery" and less towards debt
OL,18,Frepayment or financial rewards for
OL,19,Fexecutives.
