OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,FUnited Utilities was also one of six
OL,7,Fwater companies banned earlier this
OL,8,Fmonth from paying bonuses to senior
OL,9,Fbosses.
OL,11,FA new law has been introduced which
OL,12,Fwill prevent bonuses from being paid
OL,13,Fif a water company does not meet
OL,14,Fenvironmental or consumer standards,
OL,15,Fdoes not meet financial resilience
OL,16,Frequirements, or is convicted of a
OL,17,Fcriminal offence.
