OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,FThe system of fines and rewards should
OL,7,Falso focus on a reduction in pollution
OL,8,Fincidents, responsible ownership and
OL,9,Fthe need for the sector to have long-
OL,10,Fterm resilience, the MPs said.
OL,12,F"Despite some initial success after
OL,13,Fprivatisation in 1989, root-and-branch
OL,14,Freform of the water sector is now
OL,15,Fneeded to improve the sector's
OL,16,Fculture," the committee said.
