OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,FAs part of their investigation, the
OL,7,FMPs found that "public disquiet has
OL,8,Fincreasingly turned to outrage" at the
OL,9,Fway water companies and their bosses
OL,10,Fare benefiting from the sector.
OL,12,F"Over hearings with 10 of the largest
OL,13,Fwater companies and Ofwat, we
OL,14,Fregularly encountered a culture that
OL,15,Fis deaf to the crisis the sector is
OL,16,Ffacing," they said.
