OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,FCommittee chairman Alistair
OL,7,FCarmichael, a Liberal Democrat MP,
OL,8,Fsaid the sector "must not shy away
OL,9,Ffrom bold proposals" and that it has a
OL,10,F"serious culture problem".
OL,12,FHe said: "Water companies' complex and
OL,13,Fsometimes impenetrable financial
OL,14,Fstructures, with their myriad
OL,15,Fsubsidiaries, holding companies and
OL,16,Fparent organisations, seem to suggest
OL,17,Fthat their purpose is less to provide
OL,18,Fa good service to their customers and
OL,19,Fmore to allow them to juggle their
OL,20,Ffinances and their increasingly
OL,21,Funsustainable levels of debt.
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@TO]rD@AOUrD@YO]tD@JOU
