OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,F"Meanwhile, an ineffective regulatory
OL,7,Fsystem has failed to protect
OL,8,Fcustomers, the environment and the
OL,9,Ffinancial stability of the sector.
OL,11,F"It has failed to ensure that
OL,12,Fcompanies invest in essential
OL,13,Finfrastructure and it has not
OL,14,Fencouraged long-term thinking.
OL,16,F"This has got to stop now. Trust and
OL,17,Faccountability in the water sector are
OL,18,Fvery low.
