OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,F"As part of the plan for change, new
OL,7,Flegislation has banned unfair
OL,8,Fmultimillion-pound bonuses for bosses
OL,9,Fat six water companies and launched a
OL,10,Frecord 81 criminal investigations.
OL,12,F"This Government has also secured the
OL,13,Flargest investment into the water
OL,14,Fsector in history, with #104bn in
OL,15,Fprivate sector investment to clean up
OL,16,Frivers, lakes and seas and cut sewage
OL,17,Fby nearly half by 2030."
