OL,3,CWater sector needs 'root-and-branch'
OL,4,Creform, MPs say
OL,6,FA Water UK spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Everyone agrees that the water system
OL,8,Fis not working, and we have been
OL,9,Fcalling for fundamental reforms which
OL,10,Fallow investment to get quickly to
OL,11,Fwhere it needs to go.
OL,13,F"In the meantime, companies are
OL,14,Ffocused on investing a record #104
OL,15,Fbillion over the next five years to
OL,16,Fsecure our water supplies, end sewage
OL,17,Fentering our rivers and seas and
OL,18,Fsupport economic growth."
